        <mxCell id="metrics" value="Capture:&#xa;  • Queue maxsize: 1000&#xa;  • BPF: ip &amp; (tcp/udp/icmp)&#xa;  • Payload preview: 256 bytes&#xa;&#xa;Detection:&#xa;  • Rate windows: 5-60s&#xa;  • YARA gating: enabled&#xa;  • Reputation cache: 3600s&#xa;&#xa;Correlation:&#xa;  • Dedup window: 300s&#xa;  • Score cap: 100&#xa;&#xa;Storage:&#xa;  • Retention: 14 days&#xa;  • Mode: SQLite with WAL" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#666666;fillColor=#f9f9f9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=9;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=10;spacingTop=8;spacingBottom=8" vertex="1" parent="1">
